The following are [[video games]] dedicated to the construction or simulation of [[roller coaster]]s.
==Construction simulators== Many titles focused on roller coasters are [[construction and management simulation]] games. Players must construct roller coasters and sometimes other fairground attractions in order to attract visitors to their fairgrounds or otherwise achieve their goals.
